data.description: Situated On A Quiet Cul-De-Sac With Private Electronic Gated Entrance; There Awaits Your Own Personal Retreat Featuring In-Ground Gunite Pool & Spa, Main Level 3-CAR & BSMT Level 5-CAR GARAGES Have Cedar Walls & Ceilings, Epoxy Coated Floors & all are Climate Controlled. Main Level Garage Leads Directly into the Kitchen. Idyllic 1-Level Living; MASTER SUITE IS PERFECTION (1600+sf) With Separate Granite Vanities, Walk-In Closet, Jetted Tub, Double Shower, Dual Showerheads & its Own Sunroom With a Mini-Kitchen (Cabinets, Granite-tops, Sink, Mini-Fridge), Mounted TV & French Doors Lead to an AMAZING Screened Deck! Beautiful FLAGSTONE Front Porch, Steps, Driveway Accents & Pool Decking. LOVELY Professionally Designed & Low Maintenance Landscaping (NO GRASS TO CUT), Sprinkler System, Outdoor Lighting, Stained Concrete Driveway. Brand New 48KW Full House Generator! Don't Miss the Chance to put Your Touches to this Home with Unlimited Possibilities! HUGE BASEMENT both finished & unfinished.
